{"word":"G4870 - συνακολουθέω - synakolouthéō - soon-ak-ol-oo-theh'-o - Follow","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συνακολουθέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">synakolouthéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soon-ak-ol-oo-theh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Follow</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பின்செல், பின்வா"},{"paragraph":"to follow together with others, to accompany"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G190 - ἀκολουθέω - akolouthéō - ak-ol-oo-theh'-o/190\">G190</a>; to <i>accompany:</i> - follow.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1811/1811\">G1811</a>, <a href=\"#/G1872/1872\">G1872</a>, <a href=\"#/G190/190\">G190</a>, <a href=\"#/G3877/3877\">G3877</a>, <a href=\"#/G4870/4870\">G4870</a>"}]}